Comparing classes, etc.
Camera: the same. vtkm::rendering::Camera

Scene:
vtkm: vector of vtkm::rendering::Actor
vtkh: list/vector of vtkh::Renderer, batchsize, has_volume.

vtkh::Render aprox equal to vtkm::rendering::View






